label("$B$", B, SW);
label("$C$", C, SE);
label("$D$", D, S);
label("$E$", E, NE);
[/asy]

Also, triangle $CED$ is a $30^\circ$-$60^\circ$-$90^\circ$ triangle, so $DE = CD/\sqrt{3} = 10 \sqrt{3}/\sqrt{3} = \boxed{10}$.

